<refentry id="SQL-ALTERUSER">
 <refmeta>
  <refentrytitle>ALTER USER</refentrytitle>
  <manvolnum>7</manvolnum>
  <refmiscinfo>SQL - Language Statements</refmiscinfo>
 </refmeta>

 <refnamediv>
  <refname>ALTER USER</refname>
  <refpurpose>데이터베이스 롤 변경</refpurpose>
 </refnamediv>

 <indexterm zone="sql-alteruser">
  <primary>ALTER USER</primary>
 </indexterm>

 <refsynopsisdiv>
<synopsis>
ALTER USER <replaceable class="PARAMETER">이름</replaceable> [ [ WITH ] <replaceable class="PARAMETER">옵션</replaceable> [ ... ] ]

<phrase><replaceable class="PARAMETER">옵션</replaceable>에서 사용할 수 있는 것:</phrase>

      SUPERUSER | NOSUPERUSER
    | CREATEDB | NOCREATEDB
    | CREATEROLE | NOCREATEROLE
    | CREATEUSER | NOCREATEUSER
    | INHERIT | NOINHERIT
    | LOGIN | NOLOGIN
    | REPLICATION | NOREPLICATION
    | CONNECTION LIMIT <replaceable class="PARAMETER">connlimit</replaceable>
    | [ ENCRYPTED | UNENCRYPTED ] PASSWORD '<replaceable class="PARAMETER">비밀번호</replaceable>'
    | VALID UNTIL '<replaceable class="PARAMETER">timestamp</replaceable>'

ALTER USER <replaceable class="PARAMETER">이름</replaceable> RENAME TO <replaceable>새이름</replaceable>

ALTER USER <replaceable class="PARAMETER">이름</replaceable> SET <replaceable>환경설정_매개변수</replaceable> { TO | = } { <replaceable>설정값</replaceable> | DEFAULT }
ALTER USER <replaceable class="PARAMETER">이름</replaceable> SET <replaceable>환경설정_매개변수</replaceable> FROM CURRENT
ALTER USER <replaceable class="PARAMETER">이름</replaceable> RESET <replaceable>환경설정_매개변수</replaceable>
ALTER USER <replaceable class="PARAMETER">이름</replaceable> RESET ALL
</synopsis>
 </refsynopsisdiv>

 <refsect1>
  <title>설명</title>

  <para>
   <command>ALTER USER</command> 명령은 
   <xref linkend="sql-alterrole"> 명령의 별칭이다.
  </para>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1>
  <title>호환성</title>

  <para>
   <command>ALTER USER</command> 구문은
   <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> 확장 기능이다.  표준 SQL에서는
   개별 데이터베이스 시스템 고유 정의로 구현하도록 남겨 놓았다.
  </para>
 </refsect1>

